# Cursor Rules — 서울 3대 상업지구 자영업 상권분석 플랫폼 (Streamlit + Snowflake)

## Project Context
Streamlit dashboard for Seoul’s three major commercial districts — self-employed retail trade-area and location analysis. Data lives in Snowflake (SPH_DATA.GRANDATA). Korean-facing UI. Entry point: `I47AIC5MZ97CF0P5/streamlit_app.py`.

## Design System Tokens

### Colors
```
/* Cool Neutral */
--color-neutral-10: #ffffff
--color-neutral-20: #f7f7f8
--color-neutral-30: #dbdcdf
--color-neutral-40: #989ba2
--color-neutral-50: #70737c
--color-neutral-60: #5a5c63
--color-neutral-70: #292a2d
--color-neutral-80: #171719
--color-neutral-90: #0f0f10
--color-neutral-100: #000000

/* Primary Blue */
--color-primary-10: #e3effa
--color-primary-20: #cae4fa
--color-primary-30: #98ccfa
--color-primary-40: #359efa   ← main accent / CTA
--color-primary-50: #1a4e7c
--color-primary-60: #0f2c45

/* Success Green */
--color-secondary-10: #c9e1b6
--color-secondary-20: #b0e189
--color-secondary-30: #96e15c
--color-secondary-40: #7de12f  ← positive trend
--color-secondary-50: #62ad24
--color-secondary-60: #457a19

/* Error Red */
--color-error-10: #ffebeb
--color-error-20: #ffd1d1
--color-error-30: #ffb8b8
--color-error-40: #ff8585
--color-error-50: #ff5252     ← negative trend
--color-error-60: #993131
```

### Typography
```
heading1: 28px / 132% line-height
heading2: 24px / 132%
